// METBAE2 translation file
@1   = ~I am free!  I no longer feel the magical bonds of the wand around my soul!  How can I ever repay you?~
@2   = ~I think you should try to start a life for yourself.~
@3   = ~Will you add your sword to my cause?  I am trying to track down an evil wizard named Irenicus.~
